ion, you are required to correctly enter the actual number of adults, children and infants who will be occupying the accommodation. For safety and insurance reasons, we ask you to respect this number of declared occupants (baby included).<br \/>\nSARL LES DEMEURES DE VARENNES &#8211; With capital of 525,378 \u20ac &#8211; Siret: 44483134100011 Address: 2 rue de Brie &#8211; 91480 Varennes Jarcy<\/p>\n<h2>6. DOMESTIC ANIMALS<\/h2>\n<p>Animals are allowed in our accommodation (with a supplement) under the following conditions:<br \/>\n\u2022 The customer will have to pay a supplement of 8 \u20ac per night and per animal<br \/>\n\u2022 The customer must not under any circumstances use the accommodation equipment (bedding, sofa, dishes) for his animal.<br \/>\n\u2022 The client must bring all the accessories necessary for the life of his animal.<br \/>\n\u2022 Only one animal is allowed per accommodation (except in exceptional cases, contact us)<br \/>\n\u2022 The customer is responsible for the nuisance caused by his animal and assumes full responsibility: noise pollution, droppings<br \/>\n\u2022 If other guests from neighboring rooms complain about the nuisance caused by the animal, the client must take the necessary measures to put an end to this<\/p>\n<h2>7. PERSONAL EFFECTS AND ACCOMMODATION EQUIPMENT<\/h2>\n<p>It is recommended that you do not leave valuables in the rooms. The company disclaims all liability in theft case. The customer agrees to report any lost, broken, stolen or damaged equipment and is required to reimburse it.<\/p>\n<h2>8. POOL ACCESS<\/h2>\n<p>Access is available daily from 8 a.m. to 8 p.m. Drinks and meals are prohibited around the swimming pool. A nearby patio is accessible.<\/p>\n<h2>9. PROTECTION OF PERSONAL DATA<\/h2>\n<p>In accordance with European regulation 2016\/679 (RGPD), the confidentiality policy is accessible on the site: www.chateauvarennes.com in the legal notices.<\/p>\n<h2>10. COMPLAINTS AND DISPUTES<\/h2>\n<p>This contract 